## 🔐 Security Considerations

✅ **API Keys**: Keep in `.env`, never commit to git
✅ **Voice Data**: Only sent to recognized APIs (Google, Anthropic)
✅ **Storage**: Local only (reminders in ~/.voice_assistant/)
✅ **Credentials**: Can use OAuth2 for services
✅ **Privacy**: No recording storage, real-time processing only

