## 🐛 Troubleshooting Quick Ref

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Microphone not found | Check system audio settings |
| Wake word not detected | Speak clearly, check mic volume |
| No API responses | Verify internet, check API keys |
| No voice output | Check speakers, verify TTS installation |
| Commands misunderstood | Speak at normal pace in quiet environment |
| Setup fails | Ensure Python 3.8+, check error message |

